[{"question":"Yet again I ask you, Ali, what the hell is going on?","answer":"You know, Piers, every day, I get up very early.","docId":"110810pmt","qSentId":30,"aSentId":31},{"question":"Everyone has specter of Lehman Brothers hanging over them, you know?","answer":"Yes.","docId":"110810pmt","qSentId":53,"aSentId":54},{"question":"Can we see the possibility somewhere in Europe or America of banks going under of the scale of Lehman Brothers?","answer":"Well, in fact, one of the triggers today was one of Europe\u0027s largest banks, Societe Generale, losing 15 percent.","docId":"110810pmt","qSentId":55,"aSentId":56},{"question":"Is it still a sensible place to put some money right now or is it now too expensive?","answer":"When the lemmings start running towards that direction, what you want to do is run in the opposite direction.","docId":"110810pmt","qSentId":94,"aSentId":95},{"question":"Where are we, do you think?","answer":"Well, double dips are actually very, very rare.","docId":"110810pmt","qSentId":128,"aSentId":129},{"question":"What advise -- if you were writing speeches right now for President Obama, what advice would you give him now to ramp up the rhetoric in an effective way?","answer":"I think that it\u0027s worth recognizing first that this economic challenge is more than purely a rhetorical one.","docId":"110810pmt","qSentId":182,"aSentId":183},{"question":"We need the president to reconnect with his voters really, don\u0027t we?","answer":"We do.","docId":"110810pmt","qSentId":188,"aSentId":189},{"question":"Who cares what happens in France?","answer":"Well, so let me tell you exactly what happened in France.","docId":"110810pmt","qSentId":226,"aSentId":227},{"question":"Why?","answer":"Because that enables them to have growth.","docId":"110810pmt","qSentId":270,"aSentId":271},{"question":"How is he going to get Americans back to work?","answer":"I\u0027ve said this before.","docId":"110810pmt","qSentId":278,"aSentId":279},{"question":"Is this sensible or is that equally crazy?","answer":"Well, it\u0027s just emotional which makes it crazy, because it doesn\u0027t get you where you want to go.","docId":"110810pmt","qSentId":294,"aSentId":295},{"question":"Should people look to diversify into, you know, certainly more random investments?","answer":"Well, the collectibles category has never kept up with real estate or stock market category.","docId":"110810pmt","qSentId":309,"aSentId":310},{"question":"Because if you can\u0027t trust your bank, who can you trust?","answer":"Well, I agree.","docId":"110810pmt","qSentId":329,"aSentId":330},{"question":"Finally, Dave -- briefly if you don\u0027t mind -- is it ostrich time, in the sense that when these big things start exploding in this volatile way, is sometimes the best thing to do to stick your head straight in the sand and keep it there until it all blows over?","answer":"In a sense, that\u0027s true.","docId":"110810pmt","qSentId":344,"aSentId":345},{"question":"Or is that pride getting dented?","answer":"Well, I\u0027m certainly proud to be an American.","docId":"110810pmt","qSentId":378,"aSentId":379},{"question":"Do you find yourself nodding when you hear her speak?","answer":"Not her particularly.","docId":"110810pmt","qSentId":394,"aSentId":395},{"question":"Do you think the reputation of America is getting damaged badly in all this?","answer":"Yes, sure.","docId":"110810pmt","qSentId":409,"aSentId":410},{"question":"Do you think that\u0027s right?","answer":"I don\u0027t know they\u0027re the enemy.","docId":"110810pmt","qSentId":416,"aSentId":417},{"question":"Do you think more American business people should be doing that, should be looking more internally now?","answer":"I\u0027m taking the hit.","docId":"110810pmt","qSentId":427,"aSentId":428},{"question":"To actually take a hit in the way you\u0027re describing is not really the American way, is it?","answer":"I don\u0027t know that it\u0027s the American way, but it\u0027s my way.","docId":"110810pmt","qSentId":432,"aSentId":433},{"question":"What\u0027s the number one concern for them?","answer":"Paying their bills and keeping their job.","docId":"110810pmt","qSentId":440,"aSentId":441},{"question":"If you\u0027re the president, is that where you want to see the focus now, getting Americans back to work?","answer":"Yeah, I think so.","docId":"110810pmt","qSentId":444,"aSentId":445},{"question":"Did you have to do that all year?","answer":"No, I didn\u0027t thankfully.","docId":"110810pmt","qSentId":476,"aSentId":477},{"question":"Isn\u0027t he though?","answer":"ORGAN: He is.","docId":"110810pmt","qSentId":479,"aSentId":480},{"question":"Of all of those things, what was the worst, would you say?","answer":"Well, my first divorce is not on there.","docId":"110810pmt","qSentId":507,"aSentId":508},{"question":"You mean your first divorce was worse than the second wife shooting you in the chest, was it?","answer":"DKINS: It\u0027s easier to deal with somebody trying to kill you than somebody saying they don\u0027t love you anymore.","docId":"110810pmt","qSentId":512,"aSentId":513},{"question":"Did you think you were going to die?","answer":"Yeah, I do remember thinking that.","docId":"110810pmt","qSentId":520,"aSentId":521},{"question":"Yeah, I\u0027ve had some things happen to me that I didn\u0027t feel like I really deserve, you know?","answer":"Your wife, who I had the pleasure of meeting a few times on \"Apprentice\" -- delightful lady.","docId":"110810pmt","qSentId":527,"aSentId":528},{"question":"Is she well?","answer":"She remembers you hitting on her when she was up at -- and that\u0027s cool.","docId":"110810pmt","qSentId":530,"aSentId":531},{"question":"Is that -- is that the nature of the beast?","answer":"Yeah, it\u0027s part of the gig.","docId":"110810pmt","qSentId":544,"aSentId":545},{"question":"Do you still feel that?","answer":"Yeah.","docId":"110810pmt","qSentId":560,"aSentId":561},{"question":"You kind of got it all out of your system?","answer":"Yeah.","docId":"110810pmt","qSentId":562,"aSentId":563},{"question":"Does he still act as kind of a quiet motivating factor to you in your career, in your life?","answer":"You know, I would like to be able to say yes, but I\u0027ve moved now 17, 18 years past that.","docId":"110810pmt","qSentId":571,"aSentId":572},{"question":"What would he have made of what\u0027s happened to you, do you think?","answer":"Oh, he\u0027d be so proud.","docId":"110810pmt","qSentId":574,"aSentId":575},{"question":"Ali, I barely know how to ask you this, but have you got any idea what\u0027s going to happen in the markets tomorrow?","answer":"I think what you should do before the markets open is pick up some Pepto-Bismol on your way in.","docId":"110810pmt","qSentId":593,"aSentId":594}]